OL,3,CTory MP Craig Mackinlay tells of
OL,4,Closing hands and feet in sepsis ordeal
OL,6,FConservative MP Craig Mackinlay has
OL,7,Fspoken of the sepsis ordeal which left
OL,8,Fhim with both of his hands and feet
OL,9,Famputated.
OL,11,FThe South Thanet MP is due to return
OL,12,Fto Parliament for the first time today
OL,13,F(Wednesday 22 May) since he was rushed
OL,14,Finto hospital on September 28.
OL,16,FHe told the BBC he turned "a very
OL,17,Fstrange blue" shortly after being
OL,18,Fadmitted, having gone into septic
OL,19,Fshock.
