OL,3,CTory MP Craig Mackinlay tells of
OL,4,Closing hands and feet in sepsis ordeal
OL,6,FHe was almost immediately put into a
OL,7,F16-day induced coma, with his wife
OL,8,Ftold he had only a 5% chance of
OL,9,Fsurvival.
OL,11,FOn waking up, Mr Mackinlay saw his
OL,12,Farms and legs "had turned black" and
OL,13,Fwere "like a plastic" and "looked
OL,14,Fdead".
OL,16,FThe politician said he was
OL,17,F"surprisingly stoic" when he was told
OL,18,Fhe would undergo a quadruple
OL,19,Famputation on December 1.
