OL,3,CTory MP Craig Mackinlay tells of
OL,4,Closing hands and feet in sepsis ordeal
OL,6,F"They managed to save above the elbows
OL,7,Fand above the knees," he told the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster. "So you might say I'm
OL,9,Flucky."
OL,11,FIn a video recorded on the eve of the
OL,12,Foperation, obtained by The Telegraph,
OL,13,Fhe said: "The grim reaper has let me
OL,14,Fsurvive, but he's taken his payment in
OL,15,Ffour of my limbs."
OL,17,FA "sombre" Christmas followed, he told
OL,18,Fthe BBC, but he marvelled at how
OL,19,Fquickly his four-year-old daughter
OL,20,FOlivia adapted to the situation.
