OL,3,CTory MP Craig Mackinlay tells of
OL,4,Closing hands and feet in sepsis ordeal
OL,6,F"I think children are just so
OL,7,Fremarkably adjustable," he said.
OL,9,FThe 57-year-old father of one said he
OL,10,Fwants to be known as the first "bionic
OL,11,FMP" after being fitted with prosthetic
OL,12,Flegs and hands.
OL,14,FMr Mackinlay's wife Kati and daughter
OL,15,Fare set to watch his return to Prime
OL,16,FMinister's Questions from the public
OL,17,Fgallery on Wednesday.
OL,19,FThe MP is determined to fight the next
OL,20,Felection in his Kent constituency, due
OL,21,Fto be renamed Thanet East.
